data.description: Welcome to this charming manufactured home nestled on nearly an acre of serene beauty. This property offers a unique blend of comfortable living and expansive outdoor space, perfect for those seeking a peaceful retreat. Discover three spacious bedrooms that provide ample space for rest and relaxation. The layout ensures privacy and comfort for everyone in the household. With almost an acre of fenced in land, this property offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities, gardening, and creating your own private sanctuary. Enjoy the beauty of nature right at your doorstep. Schedule a showing today and experience the potential and comfort this property has to offer!
